headline: West Bancorp (WTBA) Q4 Earnings and Revenues Surpass Estimates
summary: West Bancorp (WTBA) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of +7.02% and +2.53%, respectively, for the quarter ended December 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
